INSERT INTO `movie` VALUES (1,'The Shawshank Redemption','[\"Tim Robbins\", \"Morgan Freeman\", \"Clancy Brown\"]','Frank Darabont','Frank Darabont',9.3,'[\"Drama\", \"Mystery\", \"Crime\"]','1994-09-22','2h 22min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDE3ODcxYzMtY2YzZC00NmNlLWJiNDMtZDViZWM2MzIxZDYwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjAwNDUxODI@._V1_SX300.jpg','Andy Dufresne (Tim Robbins) is sentenced to two consecutive life terms in prison for the murders of his wife and her lover and is sentenced to a tough prison. However, only Andy knows he didn\'t commit the crimes. While there, he forms a friendship with Red (Morgan Freeman), experiences brutality of prison life, adapts, helps the warden, etc., all in 19 years.'),(2,'Joker','[\"Joaquin Phoenix\", \"Robert De Niro\", \"Zazie Beetz\"]','Todd Phillips','Todd Phillips',8.5,'[\"Crime\", \"Drama\", \"Thriller\"]','2019-10-04','2h 2min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNGVjNWI4ZGUtNzE0MS00YTJmLWE0ZDctN2ZiYTk2YmI3NTYyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTkxNjUyNQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg','Forever alone in a crowd, failed comedian Arthur Fleck seeks connection as he walks the streets of Gotham City. Arthur wears two masks -- the one he paints for his day job as a clown, and the guise he projects in a futile attempt to feel like he\'s part of the world around him. Isolated, bullied and disregarded by society, Fleck begins a slow descent into madness as he transforms into the criminal mastermind known as the Joker.'),(3,'The Godfather','[\"Marlon Brando\", \"Al Pacino\", \"James Caan\"]','Francis Ford Coppola','Mario Puzo',9.2,'[\"Crime\", \"Drama\", \"Thriller\"]','1972-03-24','2h 55min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2MyNjYxNmUtYTAwNi00MTYxLWJmNWYtYzZlODY3ZTk3OTFlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzkwMjQ5NzM@._V1_SX300.jpg','Widely regarded as one of the greatest films of all time, this mob drama, based on Mario Puzo\'s novel of the same name, focuses on the powerful Italian-American crime family of Don Vito Corleone (Marlon Brando). When the don\'s youngest son, Michael (Al Pacino), reluctantly joins the Mafia, he becomes involved in the inevitable cycle of violence and betrayal.'),(4,'Inception','[\"Leonardo DiCaprio\", \"Joseph Gordon-Levitt\", \"Ellen Page\"]','Christopher Nolan','Christopher Nolan',8.8,'[\"Action\", \"Adventure\", \"Sci-Fi\"]','2010-07-16','2h 28m','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjAxMzY3NjcxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTI5OTM0Mw@@._V1_SX300.jpg','Dom Cobb (Leonardo DiCaprio) is a thief with the rare ability to enter people\'s dreams and steal their secrets from their subconscious. His skill has made him a hot commodity in the world of corporate espionage but has also cost him everything he loves. Cobb gets a chance at redemption when he is offered a seemingly impossible task: Plant an idea in someone\'s mind.'),(5,'Titanic','[\"Leonardo DiCaprio\", \"Kate Winslet\", \"Billy Zane\"]','James Cameron','James Cameron',7.8,'[\"Drama\", \"Romance\", \"Disaster\"]','1997-12-19','3h 30min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDdmZGU3NDQtY2E5My00ZTliLWIzOTUtMTY4ZGI1YjdiNjk3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTA4NzY1MzY@._V1_SX300.jpg','James Cameron\'s Titanic is an epic, action-packed romance set against the ill-fated maiden voyage of the R.M.S. Titanic; the pride and joy of the White Star Line and, at the time, the largest moving object ever built. She was the most luxurious liner of her era - the ship of dreams which ultimately carried over 1,500 people to their death in the ice cold waters of the North Atlantic in the early hours of April 15, 1912.'),(6,'Kashmir Files','[\"Anupam Kher\", \"Pallavi Joshi\", \"Anjana Sukhani\"]','Vivek Agnihotri','Vivek Agnihotri',7.2,'[\"Drama\", \"Mystery\", \"Thriller\"]','2021-08-15','2h 15m','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzJkZDIwYTAtMGU4Mi00NzU3LWI1MWItODg0M2Q1NmIxYmNlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTIyNzY0NTMx._V1_SX300.jpg','Krishna endeavours to uncover the reason behind his parents\' brutal killings in Kashmir. He is shocked to uncover a web of lies and conspiracies in connection with the massive genocide.'),(7,'The Matrix','[\"Keanu Reeves\", \"Laurence Fishburne\", \"Carrie-Anne Moss\"]','Lana Wachowski','Lana Wachowski',8.7,'[\"Action\", \"Sci-Fi\", \"Thriller\"]','1999-03-31','2h 16min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzQzOTk3OTAtNDQ0Zi00ZTVkLWI0MTEtMDllZjNkYzNjNTc4L2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjU0OTQ0OTY@._V1_SX300.jpg','When a beautiful stranger leads computer hacker Neo to a forbidding underworld, he discovers the shocking truth--the life he knows is the elaborate deception of an evil cyber-intelligence.'),(8,'The Shining','[\"Jack Nicholson\", \"Shelley Duvall\", \"Danny Lloyd\"]','Stanley Kubrick','Stephen King',8.4,'[\"Horror\", \"Drama\", \"Thriller\"]','1980-06-13','2h 26m','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWFlYmY2MGEtZjVkYS00YzU4LTg0YjQtYzY1ZGE3NTA5NGQxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@._V1_SX300.jpg','Jack Torrance (Jack Nicholson) becomes winter caretaker at the isolated Overlook Hotel in Colorado, hoping to cure his writer\'s block. He settles in along with his wife, Wendy (Shelley Duvall), and his son, Danny (Danny Lloyd), who is plagued by psychic premonitions.'),(9,'The Lion King','[\"Donald Glover\", \"Beyonce\", \"Chiwetel Ejiofor\"]','Jon Favreau','Jeff Nathanson',7.1,'[\"Animation\", \"Adventure\", \"Drama\"]','2019-07-19','1h 58m','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjIwMjE1Nzc4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDg4OTA1NzM@._V1_SX300.jpg','This Disney animated feature follows the adventures of the young lion Simba (Jonathan Taylor Thomas), the heir of his father, Mufasa (James Earl Jones). Simba\'s wicked uncle, Scar (Jeremy Irons), plots to usurp Mufasa\'s throne by luring father and son into a stampede of wildebeests. But Simba escapes, and only Mufasa is killed.'),(10,'Saving Private Ryan','[\"Tom Hanks\", \"Matt Damon\", \"Tom Sizemore\"]','Steven Spielberg','Robert Rodat',8.6,'[\"Action\", \"Drama\", \"War\"]','1998-07-24','2h 49min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjhkMDM4MWItZTVjOC00ZDRhLThmYTAtM2I5NzBmNmNlMzI1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDYyMDk5MTU@._V1_SX300.jpg','Captain John Miller (Tom Hanks) takes his men behind enemy lines to find Private James Ryan, whose three brothers have been killed in combat. Surrounded by the brutal realties of war, while searching for Ryan, each man embarks upon a personal journey and discovers their own strength to triumph over an uncertain future with honor, decency and courage.'),(11,'Killing Patient Zero','[\"Richard Berkowitz\", \" Richard Bisson\", \" Anita Bryant\"]','Laurie Lynd','Laurie Lynd, Richard A. McKay',7.5,'[\"Documentary\", \" History\"]','2020-09-17','100 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTdlNTkyOWUtMGNhNS00N2IwLWIyZjQtMmQzMTMzZDMyNWFiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTc5NDA2NzM@._V1_SX300.jpg','Gaetan Dugas, who grew up in Quebec City, was a Quebec flight attendant, who was openly and proudly gay, and he liked to wear makeup. In the early 1980s after he contracted what was initially called \"gay cancer\" in the media, he provided his blood samples and the names of seventy two (72) of his former sex partners. Gaetan Dugas was initially demonized because of his promiscuity, being openly gay, and he was wrongfully identified as patient zero, therefore being wrongfully identified for quite some time as the initial person responsible for introducing the AIDS virus into North America. Dugas\'s assistance with a subsequent medical study and his providing his sexual history played a key role in contributing to a study that helped prove HIV/AIDS was sexually transmitted.'),(12,'The Immortal Wars: Rebirth','[\"Destiny Salas\", \" Corey Taylor\", \" Lindsey Cruz\"]','Joe Lujan','Joe Lujan',4.4,'[\"Sci-Fi\"]','2020-10-01','N/A','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODBiMjc3MTQtMmRhYy00NzA2LWEzNTEtOWFkZGQwMzhiNDg2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTM0NTA5OTE@._V1_SX300.jpg','Rebirth takes place during the early brutal stages of Dominion Industries. In this story watch Olive and other deviants undergo a series of deadly experiments lead by Laurie Harvey and her team.'),(13,'India Sweets and Spices','[\"Sophia Ali\", \" Rish Shah\", \" Anita Kalathara\"]','Geeta Malik','Geeta Malik',6.1,'[\"Comedy\"]','2022-02-03','101 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODNiM2UzYzgtY2Q3Mi00NjQ5LWJhMWItOTU0MWQ3Mjg3Y2MzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTA2MDU0NjM5._V1_SX300.jpg','When college freshman Alia returns home for the summer, she discovers secrets and lies in her parents\' past that make her question everything she thought she knew about her family.'),(14,'Pilgrim\'s Progress','[\"David Thorpe\", \" John Rhys-Davies\", \" Kristyn Getty\"]','Robert Fernandez','John Bunyan, Robert Fernandez, Robert Fernandez',6.2,'[\"Animation\", \" Adventure\", \" Family\"]','2019-04-18','108 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjE4YzhjZjQtOTI3NC00M2IzLWFkNjItNDVjNzU3ODIxNmExXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjIyMjYzNjk@._V1_SX300.jpg','The epic tale of a pilgrim and his burden, based on John Bunyan\'s Masterpiece. Christian begins a journey from the City of Destruction to the Celestial City as the ultimate enemy tries everything in his power to distract him from his destination. One of the most popular books of all time is brought to life for the first time to theaters as a feature length, CGI animated movie.'),(15,'Rose Stone Star','[\"Ivana Lotito\", \" Ludovica Nasti\", \" Fabrizio Rongione\"]','Marcello Sannino','Giorgio Caruso, Guido Lombardi, Marcello Sannino',5.7,'[\"Drama\"]','2020-08-27','94 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMGE5MDgxMDktZmRhZi00N2FjLWIzYmItZGIzZDUwY2E0MWNkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTEzMjQ4NzEw._V1_SX300.jpg','Carmela is thirty, beautiful and as untamed as an horsewoman. She is jobless and struggles to get by on her own, doing small day-to-day tasks. She makes ends meet by making use of the immigrants who populate the maze of alleyways of Naples\' old historic centre. A circle of hell where, even to get a residence permit, you have to pay to work.'),(16,'Carol of the Bells','[\"RJ Mitte\", \" Lee Purcell\", \" Andrea F. Friedman\"]','Joey Travolta','J.C. Peterson',7.6,'[\"Drama\"]','2019-12-04','100 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzljMmZiNjQtYzhlNC00MThlLTk5MmQtYzM1YWFiNTEyNTQxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDQwNDM3NDA@._V1_SX300.jpg','A young man with a troubled past seeks out his biological mother. His world is turned upside down upon discovering that she is developmentally disabled. Unable to work through this new discovery on his own, the man\'s wife takes matters into her own hands forcing her husband to face the truth and heal the past.'),(17,'The Hunting','[\"Angela Cole\", \" Joelle Westwood\", \" Alan Tuskes\"]','Mark Andrew Hamer','Mark Andrew Hamer, Heather Ryan, Terrance Ryan',3,'[\"Horror\", \" Mystery\", \" Thriller\"]','2021-08-23','93 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTBlODVmYWUtYWFmYS00M2E2LTliNWYtZGUyZmQxNjBlMzdiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTY1NDQ5ODA@._V1_SX300.jpg','When a mysterious animal attack leaves a mutilated body in the forest, a conservative small town detective must enlist the help of an eager wildlife specialist to uncover the dark and disturbing truth that threatens the town.'),(18,'Coffee & Kareem','[\"Ed Helms\", \" Taraji P. Henson\", \" Terrence Little Gardenhigh\"]','Michael Dowse','Shane Mack',5.2,'[\"Action\", \" Comedy\", \" Crime\"]','2020-04-03','88 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTMyMmY0YWEtNTBkNC00NjAzLThjZjItZGFhMGYzMmU4NzE3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTMxODk2OTU@._V1_SX300.jpg','While police officer James Coffee (Ed Helms) enjoys his new relationship with Vanessa Manning (Taraji P. Henson), her beloved 12-year-old son Kareem (Terrence Little Gardenhigh) plots their break-up. Attempting to scare away his mom\'s boyfriend for good, Kareem tries to hire criminal fugitives to take him out but accidentally exposes a secret network of criminal activity, making his family its latest target. To protect Vanessa, Kareem teams up with Coffee - the partner he never wanted - for a dangerous chase across Detroit. From director Michael Dowse, COFFEE and KAREEM is an action-comedy about forging unexpected bonds, one four-letter insult at a time. Co-starring Betty Gilpin, RonReaco Lee, Andrew Bachelor and David Alan Grier.'),(19,'Star Trek Enterprise II: Der Anfang vom Ende','[\"Lars von Velsen\", \" René Dawn-Claude\", \" Sabrina Heuer-Diakow\"]','Jürgen Kaiser','Rick Berman, Brannon Braga, Sabrina Heuer-Diakow',7.3,'[\"Animation\", \" Sci-Fi\"]','2016-06-18','58 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjllNWRhMmYtMzhlZS00NjQ2LTk3ZTUtMWNlZGRiYmNiY2U5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODM5OTI2ODc@._V1_SX300.jpg','After their trip to the parallel universe, the crew of the Enterprise must determine that in the normal universe nothing is like it was. The cybernetic lifeforms of the Red Empire are there and make war against all races to elimin...'),(20,'Auntie Frog','[\"Shabnam Moghadami\", \" Afshin Hashemi\", \" Marzieh Boroomand\"]','Afshin Hashemi','Afshin Hashemi, Fereshteh Taerpoor',6.1,'[\"Adventure\", \" Comedy\", \" Family\"]','2018-06-27','81 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMGZlZmMxYTctNTQxOC00M2VmLWI1NTUtOGMyZmViNDE4MjM0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjkxOTM4ODY@._V1_SX300.jpg','Auntie Frog who has lost her twin sister along time ago is kind and friendly and patient. Lately she became more sad and impatient for her 98 children who all have left her behind. But when her grandchildren come to visit her new adventures begin to her once again.'),(21,'The Agitation','[\"Bahram Radan\", \" Mahnaz Afshar\", \" Mehran Ahmadi\"]','Fereydoun Jeyrani','Fereydoun Jeyrani',3.8,'[\"Crime\", \" Mystery\", \" Thriller\"]','2019-12-18','86 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjg0NWRhYTEtZmI0Ny00YmE5LWExYjgtYzE4NGI3MDAyNzZjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTAxODQ2NDU1._V1_SX300.jpg','The story of a twin brothers Bardia And Barbod who meet each other after many years. But during a quarrel between them Bardia who is a rich successful man gets killed. His brother Barbod replaces him and takes over everything but that will has terrible consequences for him.'),(22,'Watching This Movie Is a Crime','[\"Ali Jalilpour\", \" Mahdi Zaminpardaz\", \" Amir Aghaee\"]','Reza Zehtabchian','Reza Zehtabchian',5.4,'[\"Drama\", \" Thriller\"]','2021-01-06','91 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODVmNWJlMmQtMGZiZi00NzdlLTk5MzktOTkxNGY2YjQzYTY3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjkxOTM4ODY@._V1_SX300.jpg','Amir is a young member of Basidj and his father is a martyr of war. But when Amir\'s pregnant wife is being beaten by a stranger in the street and loses her child he decides to take action.'),(23,'Columbus','[\"Farhad Aslani\", \" Majid Salehi\", \" Saeed Poursamimi\"]','Hatef Alimardani','Hatef Alimardani',4,'[\"Comedy\", \" Drama\"]','2018-12-05','82 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzUzZDg4MDctOThkYi00NmZkLWEyOGYtMGVjM2NjMzc5MjY1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjkxOTM4ODY@._V1_SX300.jpg','A rich family are deciding to immigrate to the USA but the son of the family Manuchehr is plotting to take the money for himself instead and ruins their plan for migration.'),(24,'Lupin the Third: Fujiko Mine\'s Lie','[\"Kan\'ichi Kurita\", \" Kiyoshi Kobayashi\", \" Miyuki Sawashiro\"]','Takeshi Koike','Monkey Punch, Laura Megan Stahl, Yuuta Takahashi',6.9,'[\"Animation\", \" Adventure\", \" Crime\"]','2019-05-31','58 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BY2VjNmE0OWItZjkxOC00NmM0LTkwMzYtNjI2MDgyNzc1MjFjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDQxNjcxNQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg','Fujiko Mine is on the run with Gene, a boy who knows the location of a stash of $500 million dollars that his deceased father embezzled from the company Godfrey Mining. The boy is targeted by Bincam, an assassin hired by Godfrey Mining with a mysterious ability that allows him to bend a person\'s will. Bincam\'s whole body has been honed down from his teeth to finger nails that makes him a walking deadly weapon. So deadly that he has to be restrained when he is not hunting down targets.'),(25,'Hansa: Ek Sanyog','[\"Master Ayushman\", \" Istiyak Khan\", \" Vaishnavi Mahant\"]','Santosh Kashyap, Dhiraj Verma'