 Fazira\"]','A. Razak Mohaideen','A. Razak Mohaideen, Shukor Mohaideen, Azhari Mohd Zain',5.2,'[\"Comedy\", \" Family\", \" Romance\"]','2005-06-02','111 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWJjYzNiMzQtZGYzMC00YTNlLTg0NDAtMjI0NzZhMjI0YTg2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDM3MzU0Ng@@._V1_SX300.jpg','A girl named Sheila who is an egoist regardless of time and place. She\'s the daughter of the infamous businessman, Datuk Yusry. Sheila is handling her father\'s business efficiently but she\'s lacked of human side and was too stern ...'),(29,'Big Three Dragons','[\"Ella Chen\", \" Derek Chang\", \" Chia-Chia Peng\"]','Nancy Chen','Blanche Chiang, Nancy Chen',4.5,'[\"Comedy\"]','2019-03-21','111 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTFlZmUxZDktNzc3Zi00ODkwLWFmODEtODM1ZmM3N2U2N2MyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzYxOTQ3MDg@._V1_SX300.jpg','Rich heir Xiao-Bai turns into a poor loser after his uncle banishes him from the family, now he relies on Mahjong to win back what belongs to him.'),(30,'Kaithi','[\"Karthi\", \" Narain\", \" Arjun Das\"]','Lokesh Kanagaraj','Lokesh Kanagaraj, Pon Parthiban, Sanjeev Tiwari',8.5,'[\"Action\", \" Adventure\", \" Crime\"]','2019-10-24','145 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDYyMTk3NmYtZGJhMS00MmQxLWJhMzktZWEwMmUzNDhiZGU0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODIwMDI1NjM@._V1_SX300.jpg','On a night where the entire police officers got into an immovable situation, a paroled convict is forced to help the police, so that he can see his daughter for the first time in life. How he helps the department forms the story of this action packed entertainer.'),(31,'Scrapper','[\"Craig muMs Grant\", \" Myles Clohessy\", \" Samrat Chakrabarti\"]','Bari Kang','Bari Kang',5,'[\"Crime\", \" Drama\", \" Thriller\"]','2021-12-07','87 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDE3NGY4YjYtNGQxMC00MWIwLTkyZTEtNjQzODg0MTQzODdmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzU0NTc0OTM@._V1_SX300.jpg','Queens, New York City. A criminal playing-field of modern immigrant syndicates: human-trafficking, money-laundering and unflinching brutality. Uncomfortable in his Punjabi-American skin, ex-con turned \'scrapper\' Jake carries the weight of both his family legacy and a violent past. Caring for a mentally-challenged older brother and with a young girlfriend and an unborn child on the way, when one last job presents a way out for good, he must decide between loyalty to blood ties or to his newfound family. Is a chance at a new life worth betraying their trust? He\'ll find himself thrown into the middle of a conflict between Punjabi and Mexican factions led by violent, ruthless figures. As events explode into brutal violence, with everyone he loves at stake, he may need to go to his own darkest places one more time to finally escape.'),(32,'Herself','[\"Molly McCann\", \" Clare Dunne\", \" Ruby Rose O\'Hara\"]','Phyllida Lloyd','Clare Dunne, Malcolm Campbell',7,'[\"Drama\"]','2021-01-08','97 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWJlODA3NzgtNDc5Zi00NzJlLTgyMjMtMDI3MDAxYTVmMjQ3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTEyMjM2NDc2._V1_SX300.jpg','A young mother escapes her abusive husband and fights back against a broken housing system. She sets out to build her own home and in the process rebuilds her life and re-discovers herself.'),(33,'Jessie','[\"Ashima Narwal\", \" Sritha Chandana\", \" Atul Kulkarni\"]','Aswani Kumar V.','Aswani Kumar V.',6.8,'[\"Horror\", \" Thriller\"]','2019-03-15','106 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjc1Njc1MTMtNmMxNS00OTgxLTgzY2YtYjlhYzJkMGRmNjgwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODYzMzY3Mzc@._V1_SX300.jpg','Set in an abandoned house, the film follows a team of professional ghost hunters trying to conduct a paranormal investigation to unveil the mystery of two sisters, Jessie and Amy, where Amy shows unusual mental and physical behaviour.'),(34,'The Curse of EVE','[\"Shareen Abdullah\", \" Victoria Anderson\", \" Jasmine Deanne Andrews\"]','Jasmine Deanne Andrews','Jasmine Deanne Andrews',5.4,'[\"Horror\"]','2019-03-03','107 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjIyNTYyNTctNzFjNS00N2RiLTk0YWEtZjAxNWVjOWNjNWMwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTc1NTQ5MjQ@._V1_SX300.jpg','When a job opportunity opens up for newlywed Grant Himmel, he moves with his wife Christie out to the countryside in Courtland, Virginia. However, Christie finds life in her new house to be unsettling. The area has a history of violence and it is where the exile of the Cheroenhaka Native Americans took place; no one in the area talks about the exile however. After several strange encounters, Christie believes that the house she is living in is haunted; nobody believes her however. Then, when Christie discovers the truth behind what is really going on, she finds that she is already trapped in her house.'),(35,'BADMEN (with a good behavior)','[\"Patrick Hoffmann\", \" Loco Meisenkaiser\", \" Holger Düsterhöft\"]','Loco Meisenkaiser','Loco Meisenkaiser',6.8,'[\"Comedy\", \" Horror\"]','2018-10-13','87 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDhmODA4ZWMtYjc5My00MDRmLThjYTAtMGJlNzg4MWQ2MWI1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTY5NzI0MTQ@._V1_SX300.jpg','Jack Mauser and John Ferinio, Special Agents of the World Police, have become corrupt and lethargic over the years. Their success rate is zero, their feet are on the table, and when they talk about \'coffee with a shot\' does not mean they spend their break on the shooting range. The world seems fine until its idyllic Oldchurch City is hit by a brutal series of murders and the two incompetent cops become protagonists in a Kasperle theatre of terror. To prevent their suspension and save Oldchurch City, Mauser and Ferinio now have to fight a devilish psychopath and their own demons .'),(36,'Your Iron Lady','[\"Vanessa Benavente\", \" Alondra Lara\", \" Paloma Morales\"]','Jorge Xolalpa','Teresa Ramirez Galan, Jorge Xolalpa',8.2,'[\"Drama\"]','2020-01-23','92 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTFjYThjMWItZGRiNy00NDBmLTlkNDQtYmQ3NGU4MDBhYjljXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDE1Mjg1MTI@._V1_SX300.jpg','Set in 1998, Teresa immigrates to the U.S. to escape a 22-year abusive marriage in Mexico. With one adult child still in Mexico and three in tow, Teresa struggles to make a new life for her family in Los Angeles. Battling her selfish relatives and manipulative ex-husband, in addition to the steep challenges many immigrants face, she must learn to fight for herself and her kids in all aspects of her life. A compelling tale of resilience and the power of family, but an expertly understated work of film art.'),(37,'Lost in Klessin','[\"Lya-Amalia Grünelt\", \" Franz Klose\", \" Andreas Lessig\"]','Heintje Peter','Heintje Peter',7.5,'[\"War\"]','2018-10-27','90 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjU3ZjkyOWMtNzJlOC00YjgxLWJjZjEtNTdlNTNlZjRmY2ViXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTAwMTcyMzEw._V1_SX300.jpg','February/March 1945: While the Russians moved closer towards German home ground and towards Berlin forces were drawn to Klessin, a small village located not far from a strategic crossing over the river Oder. At the same time refugees from former German territories already in Russian control pass the area. Captain von Stock and his battle group come upon a trek of refugees and aide them find shelter and rest before they continue their journey to the West. The narration alternates between the military and political events of the time and the deeply personal relationship between Captain von Stock and a small girl who lost her mother fleeing from the approaching Red Army.'),(38,'The Queen of the Lizards','[\"Bruna Cusí\", \" Javier Botet\", \" Margot Sánchez Bassols\"]','Juan González, Nando Martínez','Juan González, Nando Martínez',4.8,'[\"Fantasy\"]','2020-11-20','63 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTUwZDNmNTYtOWQwMS00NzJmLWEyNGUtMzhiZGIyZmU1YjE2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODc0OTEyNDU@._V1_SX300.jpg','A spaceship is about to come to pick up Javi, so him and Berta have to put an end to their summer love.'),(39,'All for the Money','[\"Eugene Bush\", \" Maisha Carter\", \" Simeon Henderson\"]','Quincy Trent','Quincy Trent',5.7,'[\"Comedy\"]','2019-07-10','107 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2NmMTdmOTItNTY0YS00ZmViLTk4NDMtMjI3MzhlZjdjZGU0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTE4ODU3MTI@._V1_SX300.jpg','All for the Money...a not so every day love story of when opposites attract. When 67-year-old Eddie Wilson, who lives in his mom\'s basement, meets the thirty something, hot and classy real estate agent Simone Washington on a dating website, it seemed like love at first site.'),(40,'The Contrast','[\"Joy Villa\", \" Jermain Hollman\", \" Lee Donoghue\"]','Sean Dube, Presley Paras','Chris Johnson, Royall Tyler',4.7,'[\"Comedy\"]','2022-01-18','82 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOThlOTExNDEtOWU1Ni00MWU4LWI4ZjEtM2QxZjBmNmEzNWZiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDg2NDgxMTY@._V1_SX300.jpg','At a quaint Bed and Breakfast, Maria is about to marry her longtime beau - the smooth talking, hipster Dimple, when her Maid-of-Honor\'s brother, Colonel Henry Manly, stops by to help set up. Fate introduces them, and they connect instantly, like old friends long separated. After a touching rehearsal dinner at which Dimple shows glimmers of his formerly caring self, Maria confesses her doubts to her father, who manages to put her mind at ease. As the wedding hour approaches, truths are revealed, chaos ensues, and Maria must decide between the obligation to her family and the quickening desires of her heart.'),(41,'Enemy Lines','[\"Ed Westwick\", \" John Hannah\", \" Tom Wisdom\"]','Anders Banke','Michael Wright, Tom George',4.5,'[\"War\"]','2020-04-24','92 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjIyNzU5ZDAtODNkOS00YjU4LTk5YmMtOGVkNDY1YjA0YmI1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODY0NTMxNTE@._V1_SX300.jpg','In the frozen, war torn landscape of occupied Poland during World War II, a crack team of allied commandos are sent on a deadly mission behind enemy lines to extract a rocket scientist from the hands of the Nazis.'),(42,'American Terror Story','[\"Rim Basma\", \" Laurie Cummings\", \" Winnie Du\"]','Terry Spears','Terry Spears, Christopher Warman',2.9,'[\"Horror\"]','2019-03-01','76 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMmY2Zjk2YjUtMjgwMC00MTU0LWE2OTEtZmFlMjJkNmY5NTIzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTM3MDMyMDQ@._V1_SX300.jpg','The ghost of a young asian girl who committed suicide a century ago is awakened by a group of college students, who fall victim to their own suicides under her spell.'),(43,'Ott Tänak: The Movie','[\"Colin Clark\", \" Martin Järveoja\", \" Ivar Tänak\"]','Tarvo Mölder','Kaidi Klein',8.1,'[\"Documentary\", \" Sport\"]','2019-04-12','125 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjE5MTczNDktMzZlOS00MjMxLWIwZjAtOTNiNDA4MWI0NjFmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTEwMjQzMjk@._V1_SX300.jpg','A rare glimpse on the life and career of an otherwise reclusive World Rally Championship driver from Estonia. Often characterized as shy, retiring but headstrong, stubborn and with \"a big ego\", Ott Tänak puts all of his heart and soul into his dream of being a world champion. Hailing from the small island of Saaremaa, Tänak rallied his way into the WRC elite despite all of the adversity he faced. The documentary also features numerous interviews from relatives, friends and fellow drivers and crew members, along with vignettes from his personal life and rallying career.'),(44,'Ottam','[\"Nandu Anand\", \" Roshan Ullas\", \" Manikandan R. Achari\"]','Zam','Rajesh k Narayan',6.2,'[\"Drama\"]','2019-03-08','120 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTM0NjAzNzEtMGQ1Yy00NDIxLTk4NTAtY2RkNDE5OGZlYWJkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjkxNzQ1NDI@._V1_SX300.jpg','Set in Trivandrum, the story of Ottam unfolds in a day, and progresses through the lives of two youngsters - Abhi and Vinay. What does destiny have in store for these young men?'),(45,'Pengalila','[\"Lal\", \" Akshara Kishor\", \" Iniya\"]','T.V. Chandran','T.V. Chandran',8,'[\"Drama\"]','2019-03-08','111 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDM3MGM0NDMtMzNhZS00NDVkLTljNjItMGM3ZGE5YTViMWJiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjkxNzQ1NDI@._V1_SX300.jpg','The film highlights an unusual bond between a sixty year old Dalit worker Azhagan and an eight year old middle class girl Radha, who has moved to Kerala with her parents. Azhagan who comes to clean the backyard of her house develops a bond with Radha as she reminds her of her own sister. Together, they visit Azhagan\'s workplaces and Radha is introduced to different landscapes of the city. Within no time their bond grows stronger. Azhagan is equally liked by Radha\'s mother. However, his proximity to Radha and her mother doesn\'t go down well with Radha\'s father Vinod. Things take an ugly turn when Vinod\'s construction company decides to acquire the land that belongs to Azhagan\'s community. Will all this weaken the innocent bond that Radha and Azhagan share? Will Azhagan be able to fight for his community?'),(46,'Hand Rolled','[\"Daniel Marshall\", \" Marvin Shanken\", \" Peter Weller\"]','Steve Gherebean, Jesse Mariut','Steve Gherebean, Jesse Mariut',8.1,'[\"Documentary\"]','2019-01-30','90 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2Q0Yjg0ZmUtOTZlMC00NGMwLTg3MTQtNmNiYWJjY2FlMjVmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTk3NzI1MTA@._V1_SX300.jpg','As tensions rose between the United States and Cuba, Castro began to nationalize important industries within Cuba. The premium tobacco industry was among those nationalized and many traditional Cuban tobacco-growing families lost everything and had to flee to the US, Nicaragua, the Dominican Republic, and Honduras to rebuild. Hand Rolled follows those families on a decades-long struggle to reestablish themselves in uncertain economies throughout Latin America.'),(47,'July Kaatril','[\"Ananth Nag\", \" Anju Kurian\", \" Samyuktha Menon\"]','K.C. Sundaram','Deepthi Govindarajan, K.C. Sundaram',5.6,'[\"Drama\", \" Romance\"]','2019-03-15','162 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDk4ZmQ4NzItZDcyZi00YmZiLThjN2EtMzMwOTZmNTM5ODU5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzM4OTQzMzg@._V1_SX300.jpg','This is the story of 3 people Rajeev, Shreya and Revathi. Rajeev dates Shreya for sometime without being deeply in love but eventually gets engaged to her. Just before their wedding, he meets Revathi and finds Revathi as the love of his life and so breaks up the engagement. Rajeev is now passionately in love with Revathi. Revathi being an independent and a no-nonsense women who needs her space finds Rajeev over-imposing him on her and feels suffocated and breaks up with him. Now with all the three having had break-ups, the film is about how they move on.'),(48,'Leak (Penangkeb)','[\"Sandra\", \" Yunda\", \" Edy\"]','Mimi Jegon','Mimi Jegon',7.8,'[\"Horror\"]','2019-03-14','75 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTc1YzQxNTQtNDU3NC00NGU4LTlkNmUtNjY5NTZlOGNmYjA4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzY4NDQzNTg@._V1_SX300.jpg','Yessy, Sandra, Kayun, Edy, and Yunda want to prove the weirdness that happened in an old villa. The oddity is felt when the villa guard says that there is one room that is not rented, because it is specifically for the family of the villa owner. The mystical aura they feel, makes them try to enter a different realm. However, the terror they feel in the unseen realm forces them to return to the real world. Because of the mistakes made by Sandra, the terror continues and is increasingly frightening. With this incident, the mystery of the family room in the villa begins to unfold. There is a grandmother who lay paralyzed for five years. Grandma is deliberately exiled by the family, because the neighbors suspect grandmother of being able to become leak (evil spirits).'),(49,'The Tango of the Widower and Its Distorting Mirror','[\"Rubén Sotoconil\", \" Claudia Paz\", \" Luis Alarcón\"]','Raúl Ruiz, Valeria Sarmiento','Raúl Ruiz, Omar Saavedra Santis',6.3,'[\"Drama\"]','2020-09-23','70 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWU2NzQ4NDgtZTdlNC00OGQ4LTk0OGItMTliOTE2YTViZmE3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTAxMDQ0ODk@._V1_SX300.jpg','The story of a man whose wife has committed suicide and appears to him as a ghost, following him everywhere and changing his personality.'),(50,'The Other Side of the Wind','[\"John Huston\", \" Oja Kodar\", \" Peter Bogdanovich\"]','Orson Welles','Orson Welles, Oja Kodar',6.7,'[\"Drama\"]','2018-11-02','122 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDg5NTQ0NDU1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTExNzIyNjM@._V1_SX300.jpg','A famed, and infamous, movie director, JJ Hannaford, dies in a car accident. He was about to release his latest movie and a documentary camera crew had been following him around in the days preceding his death. We see the events leading up to his death, the careers Hannaford destroyed, the enemies he made and his last film, The Other Side of the Wind.'),(51,'The Wandering Soap Opera','[\"Luis Alarcón\", \" Patricia Rivadeneira\", \" Francisco Reyes\"]','Raúl Ruiz, Valeria Sarmiento','Pía Rey, Raúl Ruiz',6.5,'[\"Comedy\", \" Drama\", \" Fantasy\"]','2019-05-17','80 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTdlYWQyY2QtOWUxZC00YmRmLWJmNTYtZmY0NDM0NmI5MDQ2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTAxMDQ0ODk@._V1_SX300.jpg','The film revolves around the concept of soap opera. Its structure is based on the assumption that Chilean reality does not exist, but rather is an ensemble of soap operas. There are four audiovisual provinces, and the threat of war is felt among the factions. The political and economic problems are immersed in a fictional jelly divided into evening episodes. The entire Chilean reality is viewed from the point of view of the soap opera, which acts as a revealing filter of this same reality.'),(52,'Angeschwemmt','[\"Josef Fuchs\", \" Vickerl Albrecht\", \" Kastner Herbert\"]','Nikolaus Geyrhalter','Nikolaus Geyrhalter',7.2,'[\"Documentary\"]','2023-03-03','86 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQ3Mzc0MTUxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODI4MTcwMg@@._V1_SX300.jpg','\'Washed up\' presents a portrait of people who spend their lives on the banks of the river Danube or on the river itself. (Robert Buchschwenter)'),(53,'A Dangerous Practice','[\"James Faulkner\", \" Juliana Paes\", \" Antonio Saboia\"]','Gustavo Fernández','Jaqueline Vargas',7.1,'[\"Drama\"]','2022-02-24','108 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzQzZGQwYmYtMWEyNy00MjZkLWE5OTAtYmIyNDg1NTRiMDdjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTEyMjMxNw@@._V1_SX300.jpg','Based on a true story. Arigo, an uneducated man, happily married, father of six, is chosen by a mysterious force to rise up as a spiritually and supernaturally gifted surgeon. Miraculously healing thousands of desperate people, he now faces the scorn of the medical profession and his beloved Catholic church. Charged with crimes against the people his future is uncertain. Arigo, a simple, caring and deeply loving man who never sought fame or fortune, and whose encounters with multitudes of people, rich and poor, resulted in extraordinary healings beyond the explanation of medical science. The contrasting worlds of small town life in Brazil, politics, the Church and a penetrating voyage into the unknown, are played against a story line exposing the vulnerability of the human condition in all its characteristics and an eventual triumph against accepted beliefs.'),(54,'Joe Finds Grace','[\"Anthony Harrison\", \" C. Ernst Harth\", \" Ellie Harvie\"]','Anthony Harrison','Anthony Harrison',8.6,'[\"Animation\", \" Adventure\", \" Comedy\"]','2017-04-22','83 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2M0ODZjOWYtMmIzYS00MzQxLThjMzctZmNlNDAzYThjYjNjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDAyMTY3Nw@@._V1_SX300.jpg','A comic drama about simple-minded Joseph Briteman, a disfigured institute patient who wanders off into an animated world of fantasy and reality in search of his long lost sister. His quest leads him to an encounter with a kind-hearted film star who unwittingly brings him into her unique world of make-believe. In the end, it is a near-death experience that finally forces Joseph to accept the truth regarding his sister\'s disappearance.'),(55,'Heaven & Hell','[\"Cheryl M. Lynn\", \" David Carter\", \" Bill Collard\"]','Stuart Paul','Stuart Paul',4,'[\"Drama\"]','2018-11-06','104 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWM5NWY5YzItZDViZC00YzgwLTk4NzctZDdiZGE5MTY5M2QwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjI5Mjk4MjU@._V1_SX300.jpg','In 1990s Los Angeles, danger lurks around the corner after a freak accident leaves an undercover cop with supernatural abilities while also unleashing a horror that he must destroy before it destroys everything.'),(56,'Holy Hollywood','[\"Tony Leech\", \" Timothy Muskatell\", \" Tony Tarantino\"]','Terry Zarchi','Terry Zarchi',6.1,'[\"Comedy\"]','2021-10-31','82 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGFmMjViYzYtZTA2YS00ODVmLTkwYzktNjA1NjlkN2YyZmExXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTM1Mjk1MTU0._V1_SX300.jpg','Two best friends open up an extras casting agency only to find out that some people will kill to make it in Hollywood.'),(57,'Over-sexed Rugsuckers from Mars','[\"Richard Monda\", \" Jean Stewart\", \" Billybob Rhoads\"]','Michael Paul Girard','Michael Paul Girard',3.1,'[\"Comedy\", \" Sci-Fi\"]','2022-10-08','87 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWU4ZmYyZDQtM2RiZS00ODFhLTkzNjAtOTcyNTU2ZGQ0MjMyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQ2MjQyNDc@._V1_SX300.jpg','Aliens return to earth after 10 million years to see what has become of the human experiment they have created only to be disappointed by what they find. After landing they come upon Vernon a homeless bum and decide that earthlings are untidy and figure crossing a vacuum and a human will elimate the problem as well as create a better race of beings. The experiment however goes awry after one of the aliens pee in Vernon\'s bottle of gin which makes him insanely in love with the vacuum Dusty which was brought to life by the aliens. Things get a tad bit crazy from here as Dusty tries to reproduce and Vernon tries hard to find Dusty.'),(58,'Parinati','[\"Basant Josalkar\", \" Surekha Sikri\", \" Sudhir Kulkarni\"]','Prakash Jha','H. Banerjee, Vijayadan Detha',7.1,'[\"Drama\"]','2020-05-21','125 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTExMjU3Y2MtZDdhMy00NWJiLWI5MzktZWJhMTFiN2FjNTFjXkEyXk