ky','Susanna Alperina, Aleksandr Brunkovsky',4.8,'[\"Documentary\"]','2018-09-10','104 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzZiY2Y1ZDAtZjNjOS00MTI5LTkzNTgtOWZjNmU3YmZkM2NhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDY3OTI3NDE@._V1_SX300.jpg','In the world, there is a city-port Odessa, which was specially created as a refuge for people of different nationalities and religions. Humor is a special language that helps people from Odessa to communicate and get along with each other. Legends are spreading about Odessa\'s humor and accent. But - a paradox - people are constantly leaving it. It is loved, but it is left as a child leaves his mother. On the example of this city and its inhabitants, film creators wanted to understand - why people flee from their cities. Authors tried to find the answer taking pictures of Odessa citizens in Germany, Israel, Ukraine, Russia, Austria, France and other places. Michael Zhvanetskij, Roman Kartsev, Leonid Barats and Rostislav Khait, Victor Loshak, Oksana Fandera, Valerij Todotovskij, Mikhail and Anatoly Kontush and many others are telling their stories and giving their opinions on what is the phenomenon of the city by the Black Sea.'),(537,'Quando as Luzes das Marquises se Apagam - a História da Cinelândia Paulistana','[\"Nabil Bouduki\", \" Carlos Augusto Calil\", \" Inimá Simões\"]','Renato Brandão','Renato Brandão',7.5,'[\"Documentary\"]','2018-04-17','81 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNWUwNjM2NWMtMGQ2YS00Mjg3LWFmMTEtYmU2OWM5YWEwZGYzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTAxMzcxODUx._V1_SX300.jpg','A documentary on the history of the movie theaters in São Paulo and, by telling this story, also about urban life in downtown region of the great city. Very good research.'),(538,'Odessa','[\"Evgeniy Tsyganov\", \" Leonid Yarmolnik\", \" Irina Rozanova\"]','Valeriy Todorovskiy, Irina Tretyakova','Maksim Belozor, Dmitry Ivanov, Valeriy Todorovskiy',6.3,'[\"Comedy\", \" Romance\"]','2019-09-05','130 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2RhNjNiMDctOTRmN