mpolite and smelly, sneaks into Henri\'s house. Despite the attempts of the whole family to throw him out, and that his wife\'s unconditional love begin to falter, this dog, whom they decide to call \"Stupid,\" is going to become Henri\'s best friend.'),(545,'Das perfekte Geheimnis','[\"Wotan Wilke Möhring\", \" Jessica Schwarz\", \" Elyas M\'Barek\"]','Bora Dagtekin','Bora Dagtekin, Paolo Genovese, Filippo Bologna',6.6,'[\"Comedy\", \" Drama\", \" Romance\"]','2019-10-31','120 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMmEwMjRiYjItYmZjNi00NzM0LWI3MzItMTFhMTc4NTRjNmU0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDU5MDEyMA@@._V1_SX300.jpg','Three women and four men: Everyone has a mobile phone, which makes a total of seven mobile phones. When the friends come together for dinner one evening, they suddenly come up with an idea. They play a game: Everyone puts their cell phone in the middle of the table and no matter who gets which pictures or messages sent, no matter how brief - everything has to be shared with the others. Telephone calls are only allowed via the loudspeaker. But what starts as an entertaining pastime, which should bring a little tension in the evening, soon leads to some embarrassing and tense situations full of surprises. And soon, not only the mood threatens to tilt, the long-standing relationships are at stake through the discovery of explosive lies and secrets at stake.'),(546,'Skin Deep: The Battle Over Morgellons','[\"Cindy Casey\", \" Steven R. Feldman\", \" Marianne Middelveen\"]','Pi Ware','Pi Ware',7.2,'[\"Documentary\"]','2020-04-05','90 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMGJhMDM5ZjMtOTliOS00MDkxLWFhMzEtYWY5NzRlODg2OGJjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODI1NzMyODk@._V1_SX300.jpg','A nurse journeys to discover the truth behind Morgellons, a disease so bizarre, patients who suffer from it are regularly written off as delusional by doctors and loved ones. But who is delusional, the patients who believe or the doctors who deny?'),(547,'In the Name of Peace: John Hume in America','[\"Tony Blair\", \" Jimmy Carter\", \" Bill Clinton\"]','Maurice Fitzpatrick','Maurice Fitzpatrick',7.2,'[\"Documentary\"]','2017-07-13','90 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjQxZTYxOTUtZTA1NS00ZDVhLWFkMmUtZGUzMGNhMTM4MGI3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjUxMjc1OTM@._V1_SX300.jpg','Through the relationships he cultivated with The White House and US Congress, John Hume created the framework for peace in Northern Ireland.'),(548,'Kerosin','[\"Valeri Maslov\", \" Evgenija Molotova\", \" Vasilisa Simualis\"]','Yusup Razykov','Yusup Razykov',6.4,'[\"Drama\"]','2020-03-26','77 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDc1MzA1YmUtOTBjNS00ZmZiLWE0NGMtYmZmZTVlYjA2YzNlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjk1NzAxNg@@._V1_SX300.jpg','The fantastic story about the power of simple people, capable of living and surviving in the most complex circumstances, about love, loyalty and beauty.'),(549,'Doberman','[\"Maruja Bustamante\", \" Mónica Raiola\", \" Andrea Strenitz\"]','Azul Lombardía','Azul Lombardía',5.9,'[\"Drama\"]','2019-05-16','72 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDQ2MWZhY2QtNjEwNC00YmJhLWE1NmUtMzNjMDBlY2YwOTNkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQwNjAwNjQ@._V1_SX300.jpg','A nap afternoon in the outskirts of town. The worlds of two women intertwine, going from a casual conversation to a battle field, without being able to avoid the inevitable: a domestic tragedy.'),(550,'On the Edge','[\"Svetlana Khodchenkova\", \" Stasya Miloslavskaya\", \" Sergey Puskepalis\"]','Eduard Bordukov','Eduard Bordukov, Aleksandr Egorov, Igor Gordashnik',6.3,'[\"Drama\", \" Sport\"]','2020-11-26','115 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTY0ODlhMjYtMDYxNi00NTRhLTk2MWUtZjRhZmJiMjc1ZmM4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODAyNDY5MzU@._V1_SX300.jpg','The film\'s two main protagonists are Russia\'s best saber fencers. One of them has long been in the limelight, the other only recently made it into the national team and has been winning almost every tournament since. The two athletes begin to fight for supremacy both on and off