zed as one of the most important museums in the entire world, turning it in a treasure of incalculable value and heritage of culture for all human kind (rulers, painters, artists, architects, collectors, engineers, curators, physics, intellectuals, historians...), that it tells the story not only a country, but a continent. As Goya said, \"when abandoned by reason, imagination produces impossible monsters; united with her, she is the mother of the arts and the origin of their wonders.\"'),(805,'Don\'t Click','[\"Valter Skarsgård\", \" Mark Koufos\", \" Catherine Howard\"]','G-Hey Kim','Courtney Ellum',2.8,'[\"Horror\"]','2020-12-11','77 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTg1MmM0MDktZTc3NC00ZTVkLWE0NjgtYmU1MzdhODY5MDJkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTg1MTU3OTk@._V1_SX300.jpg','After coming back home from a party, Josh notices that his roommate Zane has disappeared although supposed to stay home tonight. Zane\'s laptop screen starts flashing and that\'s the last thing Josh can remember as he groggily wakes up to find mutilated Zane in a dank, surreal chamber with no way out. Josh tries everything he can to save both his friend and himself from a dangerous entity that begins to take control of their bodies and minds.'),(806,'Transference','[\"Lauren Buglioli\", \" Tyner Rushing\", \" Amelie McLain\"]','Aditya J. Patwardhan','Nicole Cannon',4.7,'[\"Horror\", \" Thriller\"]','2020-08-07','79 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWNhNjMwYzUtMmUwNS00ZTUwLTkwNzMtOGYxYjRjNTkyZDlkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzkxMzcxNQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg','When her estranged father dies, a trauma therapist\'s haunted memories manifest as she finds the courage to face her demons and lay them to rest.Plot summaryAdd synopsis'),(807,'Always Miss You','[\"Amber Kuo\", \" Ryan Zheng\", \" Dongxue Li\"]','Hung-i Chen, Chen Hung-i, Haozhou Qiu','Hung-i Chen',3.9,'[\"Romance\"]','2019-05-03','98 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWJkMDc5YjEtMjUzOS00MWEzLTg1YzEtZjFlZTg1ZTU1YjU2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzI1Nz