ick White','John Ainslie, Svyatoslav Podgaevskiy, Patrick White',3.7,'[\"Horror\"]','2021-06-15','91 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTFlM2ExYjItYmVmNi00ZGJlLWI0NTAtNWEzZDRkNWM2ZmZiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTMzOTMzMTg@._V1_SX300.jpg','According to legend, an ominous entity known as the Queen of Spades can be summoned by performing an ancient ritual. Those brave enough draw a door and a staircase on a mirror, in darkness, and say her name three times. What happens next must be experienced to be believed. Four teenagers decide to summon the Queen of Spades as a joke. But they could never imagine the horrors this innocent prank has condemned them and their loved ones too. The evil entity won\'t stop until she gets their souls.'),(890,'The Promised Land','[\"Gô Ayano\", \" Akira Emoto\", \" Shizuka Ishibashi\"]','Takahisa Zeze','Shûichi Yoshida, Takahisa Zeze',5.9,'[\"Crime\", \" Drama\"]','2019-10-18','129 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOWJkNTNhODAtZDJkOS00MWExLTgzYzEtOGNiMzJmZDA0ZjA2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjE4OTY3NTg@._V1_SX300.jpg','A girl is kidnapped and the perpetrator roams freely. When a similar case occurs along the same road and in similar circumstances a suspect is identified leading to the accused running away and going into hiding. Another year on and another man falls into suspicion. It is too much to bear and a burden to carry, but with suspicion all around and no culprits apprehended the situation is somewhat understandable.'),(891,'Queen of Snakes','[\"Stephanie Mihm\", \" Rachel Grubb\", \" Michael G. Kaiser\"]','Christopher R. Mihm','Christopher R. Mihm',4,'[\"Thriller\"]','2019-04-24','69 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2FjNzdmYWUtZTIzMy00Yzk3LThkNDctMDUyYTk4Y2NkZTU2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTE0NDk4NA@@._V1_SX300.jpg','Angry at her daughter/caretaker for being directly responsible for her paraplegia, the reclusive Mrs. Crawford accidentally receives a package containing a mysterious amulet. The ancient treasure grants her the horrific powers of a lesser Norse goddess known as the Queen of Snakes and, in a quest to control them, becomes a danger to herself...and potentially the ENTIRE WORLD.'),(892,'Pitkä perjantai','[\"Janne Pikka\", \" Karim Saheb\", \" Miika Tuohimaa\"]','Karim Saheb','Janne Pikka, Karim Saheb, Miika Tuohimaa',5.2,'[\"Action\", \" Comedy\"]','2019-05-17','114 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTcyZWMyMmEtMmIyMy00MTg2LWJjNWEtMWRlOWUyM2IwZjQzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTAyNTMyODM2._V1_SX300.jpg','Australian mega-corporation SuperCon is acquiring media companies around the globe. Radio Treble is also in danger of being swallowed by the monopoly. Ari, Leo and Otto, are sent to Sydney to try and save the jobs. They may not be the negotiators that the situation would require, but they are the only negotiators available. It\'s the end of the world as they know it and the future of the whole company lays on their shoulders.'),(893,'Boys from County Hell','[\"Jack Rowan\", \" Nigel O\'Neill\", \" Louisa Harland\"]','Chris Baugh','Chris Baugh, Brendan Mullin',5.9,'[\"Comedy\", \" Horror\"]','2021-08-06','88 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDBiM2RhODAtYjFlNi00NWNiLWEyZDEtMGZiYjRiMWMxMzllXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjI0NTQ2Nw@@._V1_SX300.jpg','A crew of hardy road workers, led by a bickering father and son, must survive the night when they accidentally awaken an ancient Irish vampire.'),(894,'Brown Boys','[\"Hans Masoe\", \" Lagi Farani\", \" Johnny Aukusitino\"]','Hans Masoe','Hans Masoe',3.8,'[\"Comedy\"]','2019-05-02','92 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDZmM2JlOTItNzlhYy00ZDAwLThjMDYtNzY4NGY1OGYyNmZjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTExNDQ2MTI@._V1_SX300.jpg','A coming-of-age film about six Samoan men growing up in South Auckland, New Zealand.'),(895,'Roh Fasik','[\"Evan Sanders\", \" Irwansyah\", \" Denira Wiraguna\"]','Ubay Fox','Ubay Fox, Evelyn Afnilia',6.2,'[\"Horror\"]','2019-05-09','90 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2JhMTRiM2MtMmYzOC00YTk1LWEyZTUtMzUzYThjOWMz