y wanted to give this film a try, but I just couldn\'t keep watching because it\'s so boring. If they have chosen to present the story in the other way, I mean if they could do it not to seem like it\'s boring, yeah, this film might turn out to be a fine film.'),(1195,'Zhou Enlai Returned To Yanan','[\"Wei Huang\", \" Jin Liu\", \" Qi Lu\"]','Jin Liu, Weidong Wu','Qingwei Wang, Jun Yang',5.3,'[\"Biography\", \" History\"]','2019-05-15','103 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWUyOTFkZTQtZTRlOC00YzFkLWJhNWUtZTM2MmUwM2U3M2MxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTM0MDc1ODE@._V1_SX300.jpg','This propaganda film uses the unique perspective of Premier Zhou Enlai, looking back on the 13-year major historical event of the Chinese Revolution during the Yan\'an period.'),(1196,'Wa\'alaikumussalam Paris','[\"Boris Bokir\", \" Nino Fernandez\", \" Fransoa\"]','Benni Setiawan','Benni Setiawan',8.8,'[\"Comedy\", \" Drama\", \" Romance\"]','2016-03-17','106 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjI3OGY3NTMtYTJlMy00MGEwLTllODUtZGFiZWRjMWM4NGExXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjU0ODQ5NTA@._V1_SX300.jpg','Itje (Velove Vexia), a village girl hopes her life will change drastically after marrying a French man, Clement (Nino Fernandez).'),(1197,'Nightlife','[\"Julian Looman\", \" Elyas M\'Barek\", \" Frederick Lau\"]','Simon Verhoeven','Simon Verhoeven',5.7,'[\"Comedy\", \" Romance\"]','2020-02-13','111 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYmZlNjIxZWItY2JkYy00YmJkLWIxYzctNjc1NzU4OTk3MjM3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQ1MTgwOA@@._V1_SX300.jpg','Milo works as a bartender in Berlin. If he is not just turning the day into night and then continuing to party, he wakes up in bed with strange women and watches others how they lead a completely normal life in daylight. One night he meets his dream wife Sunny through a series of coincidences. She loves music more than anything and was offered an offer by her boss to work for a music label in Atlanta. The next week they should go to the USA. The two meet for a date the s