lk in the mountains, the couples, strangers to each other, arrived in a mythic burial place called Sad Hill, where they had to face the naked facts of their hollow marriages in a totally new psychological light. The wives started the same walking ballet as did Clint Eastwood, Lee van Cleef and Eli Wallach in Leone\'s film. In a few minutes, the lives of the couples would change completely.'),(1203,'Roundabout, the Shortest Distance Is Round','[\"Ryohei Shioguchi\", \" Mukai Riku\", \" Hattori Muo\"]','Daisuke Yamanouchi','Daisuke Yamanouchi',6.8,'[\"Drama\", \" Romance\"]','2019-07-05','70 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWM1MzZkZTgtODI2MS00NWExLWJkNDgtNmU0ZDJkYzFmMDFmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTQwNDIzNzA@._V1_SX300.jpg','Haruto spends a lonely high school. The new teacher, Aoyama, cares about him and starts an exchange diary. Haruto gradually opens up, but one day, when he was resting because of a cold, he was kissed by Aoyama who came to visit him. Agitated by the sudden incident, Haruto violently refused and Aoyama was chased away from teaching. Three years later: Haruto, who graduated from high school and became a host, has debts and sells his body. But suddenly he meets Aoyama again.'),(1204,'My Best Friend Anne Frank','[\"Aiko Beemsterboer\", \" Josephine Arendsen\", \" Zsolt Trill\"]','Ben Sombogaart','Marian Batavier, Paul Ruven',6.2,'[\"Drama\"]','2021-09-09','103 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTk5OTM2YTYtN2Y3Ny00ODZjLWFmNTgtZGVhMDM4NmYzMGE0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTQ1OTUwMzA@._V1_SX300.jpg','Hannah is imprisoned at camp Bergen Belzen days before being liberated, where she thinks back of her time in Amsterdam with her best friend Anne the first few years of the war. Hannah finds out Anne is also in the camp, separated ...'),(1205,'A1','[\"Santhanam\", \" Tara-Alisha Berry\", \" Motta Rajendran\"]','K. Johnson','K. Johnson',5.2,'[\"Comedy\", \" Drama\"]','2019-07-26','109 min','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGU4MzRjNGItYWVkOS00OWU5LTkxY